response.overview: Since its inception in 1968, Deep Purple has toured the world over and over again, with few interruptions. Latest opus to date, Whoosh! follows two albums that had already charted worldwide, inFinite (2017) and NOW What?! (2013) . Concert filmed on July 18, 2023 at the Jazzopen festival in Stuttgart, Germany.
response.title: Deep Purple - Jazz Open Stuttgart 2023
